    <item>
      <title>花旗集团考虑为 Berry 和 Glatfelter 提供 20 亿美元债务方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/citi-eyes-2-billion-debt-package-for-berry-glatfelter-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团和富国银行据知情人士透露，公司正在准备一项 20 亿美元的债务计划，以支持 Berry Global Group Inc. 将其大部分健康、卫生和特色业务分拆给 Glatfelter Corp.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/citi-eyes-2-billion-debt-package-for-berry-glatfelter-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 20:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾因霍恩的 Greenlight 上季度表现落后于“崩溃”的股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/einhorn-s-greenlight-underperformed-broken-stock-market-last-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大卫·艾因霍恩 (David Einhorn) 的绿光资本 (Greenlight Capital) 在年初的一封致投资者的信中表示，其表现落后于“根本崩溃”的股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/einhorn-s-greenlight-underperformed-broken-stock-market-last-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 19:44:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瓦莱罗预计墨西哥燃料需求将增长，尽管多斯博卡斯增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/valero-sees-mexican-fuel-demand-growing-despite-dos-bocas-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瓦莱罗能源公司预计墨西哥的燃料需求将增长，尽管旗舰多斯博卡斯炼油厂将提高国内产量，而且总统领跑者提议转向更多的绿色能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/valero-sees-mexican-fuel-demand-growing-despite-dos-bocas-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 19:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Syensqo 首席执行官谈佐治亚工厂奠基仪式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-24/syensqo-ceo-on-georgia-plant-groundbreaking-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[化学品制造商 Syensqo 准备于明天在佐治亚州奥古斯塔的工厂破土动工，该工厂将成为北美最大的聚偏二氟乙烯产能生产设施。首席执行官伊尔哈姆·卡德里 (Ilham Kadri) 与埃德·勒德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 和卡罗琳·海德 (Caroline Hyde) 就“彭博科技”进行了对话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-24/syensqo-ceo-on-georgia-plant-groundbreaking-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
